          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wren Kitchens</strong> — a popular choice across the Midlands; Pindi fits Wren independently, without being tied to their retailer installation scheme. See the <a href="/retailers/wren/" style="color: var(--teal);">Wren installation page</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Howdens Joinery</strong> — Pindi has a trade account with Howdens, giving him direct depot access. See the <a href="/retailers/howdens/" style="color: var(--teal);">Howdens installation page</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Magnet</strong> — a common choice for Bedworth homeowners seeking mid-range quality; all Magnet ranges are fully compatible with independent installation.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>IKEA</strong> — IKEA's METOD system is fitted regularly across the area; Pindi is well-versed in IKEA's assembly and installation method.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wickes and B&Q</strong> — both popular with homeowners fitting to a budget; Pindi brings the same attention to detail regardless of the kitchen's price point.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Benchmarx, DIY Kitchens, Kutchenhaus, Symphony, Masterclass</strong> — all covered as standard.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Premium brands</strong> — including Häcker, Nobilia, and Mereway, fitted to the highest standard wherever required across the area.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          If your kitchen brand is not listed, call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> — in almost every case it can be accommodated.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <SupplierLogos />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Areas Covered -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Areas of Bedworth and CV12 Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi covers the whole of the Bedworth area within the CV12 postcode, as well as the adjacent settlements immediately south of Nuneaton. He regularly works across:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Bedworth Town &amp; Surrounds</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Bedworth town centre</strong> — post-war terraces and semis, many in galley layouts</li>
              <li><strong>Exhall</strong> — established residential estate, mixed post-war housing</li>
              <li><strong>Ash Green</strong> — semi-rural village with varied property types</li>
              <li><strong>Bulkington</strong> — village south-east of Bedworth, period and modern properties</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Wider CV12 Coverage</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Goodyears End</strong> — residential area on the south-west edge of Bedworth</li>
              <li><strong>Hawkesbury</strong> — village settlement between Bedworth and Coventry</li>
              <li><strong>Longford</strong> — north Coventry suburb close to the Bedworth border</li>
              <li>All CV12 postcodes covered as standard</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Visit the <a href="/areas/bedworth/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">Bedworth area page</a> for more detailed information, or call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> to confirm your postcode is covered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: What's Included & Pricing -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          What's Included in a Kitchen Fit — and How Pricing Works
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          A full kitchen fitting service from Pindi Sahota covers the complete installation from stripped room to finished kitchen. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 pl-1" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Stripping out the existing kitchen, including disconnecting the sink and removing appliances</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Levelling and setting out all base units to achieve a perfectly flat worktop run — critical in older Bedworth properties with uneven floors</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Fitting all wall and base carcasses, doors, drawers, hinges, and soft-close mechanisms</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Cutting wall units to height where ceiling clearances are restricted — a common requirement in Bedworth's lower-ceiling post-war properties</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Cutting and fitting laminate, solid timber, or stone worktops, including scribed end panels</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Sink and tap installation, including connection to existing waste and supply pipework</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Installation and connection of integrated appliances — dishwashers, fridges, ovens, hobs, and extractors</span>
          </li>
